Package: OAmetrics
Type: Package
Title: Bibliometric Indices Based on the OpenAlex API
Version: 0.4.7
Authors@R: 
    person("Felix D.", "Schönbrodt", , "felix.schoenbrodt@psy.lmu.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8282-3910"))
Maintainer: Felix Schönbrodt <felix.schoenbrodt@psy.lmu.de>
Description: Computes several bibliometric indices by calling the OpenAlex database API, including journal impact factors, h-indexes, field normalized citation scores (FNCS) and normalized percentage ranks. Provides indizes for co-author networks (e.g., internationalization) and citation metrics by calling the BIP! database.
